org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model.util

Class DetailViewAdapterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • AdapterFactoryImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model.util.DetailViewAdapterFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DetailViewItemProviderAdapterFactory

    public class DetailViewAdapterFactory
extends AdapterFactoryImpl
    The Adapter Factory for the model. It provides an adapter createXXX method for each class of the model.
